WEBVTT

1
00:00:12.804 --> 00:00:15.076
Tell your daughters of this year,
与您女儿谈谈，在过去的一年。

2
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.196
how we woke needing coffee
我们是如何依赖咖啡苏醒，

3
00:00:17.220 --> 00:00:21.036
but discovered instead cadavers strewn about our morning papers,
却发现尸体在晨报上看到，

4
00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:25.860
waterlogged facsimiles of our sisters, spouses, small children.
悲剧同样也来自于我们的姐妹、伴侣和年少的孩子。

5
00:00:26.420 --> 00:00:30.036
Say to your baby of this year when she asks, as she certainly should,
当她问起，你要告诉她这一年发生了什么，她当然应该问

6
00:00:30.060 --> 00:00:31.636
tell her it was too late coming.
告诉她，这一切来的太晚了。

7
00:00:31.660 --> 00:00:36.116
Admit even in the year we leased freedom, we didn't own it outright.
承认吧，即使在我们获得自由的日子里，却没能全部地拥有。

8
00:00:36.140 --> 00:00:38.956
There were still laws for every way we used our privates
我们的个人生活的林林总总被法律所桎梏

9
00:00:38.980 --> 00:00:41.476
while they pawed at the soft folds of us,
他们抚弄我们柔软的褶皱

10
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:44.235
grabbed with no concern for consent,
违背我们的意愿去抓弄

11
00:00:44.259 --> 00:00:46.876
no laws made for the men that enforced them.
与此同时，对于男性却没有同样的规则

12
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:49.316
We were trained to dodge,
我们被迫学会了躲避，

13
00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:51.956
to wait, to cower and cover,
等待、退缩、掩饰，

14
00:00:51.980 --> 00:00:54.876
to wait more, still, wait.
以及无尽地等待

15
00:00:54.900 --> 00:00:56.780
We were told to be silent.
我们被要求保持沉默。

16
00:00:57.260 --> 00:00:59.516
But speak to your girls of this wartime,
但是，跟你女儿讲讲这战争时期，

17
00:00:59.540 --> 00:01:02.116
a year preceded by a score of the same,
和往昔无异的一年

18
00:01:02.140 --> 00:01:04.396
so as in two decades before,
也和二十年前无异的一年

19
00:01:04.420 --> 00:01:05.956
we wiped our eyes,
我们拭去泪水，

20
00:01:05.980 --> 00:01:07.876
laced caskets with flags,
在棺材上铺好旗帜

21
00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:10.076
evacuated the crime scene of the club,
疏散犯罪现场

22
00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:11.396
caterwauled in the street,
在街道上疾呼

23
00:01:11.420 --> 00:01:14.716
laid our bodies on the concrete against the outlines of our fallen,
躺在水泥地上，紧挨着我们倒下的身影，

24
00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:16.675
cried, "Of course we mattered,"
哭喊着，“我们女性当然很重要，”

25
00:01:16.699 --> 00:01:18.076
chanted for our disappeared.
为我们所失去的吟唱。

26
00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:19.700
The women wept this year.
今年女性又在哭泣

27
00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:21.476
They did.
哭泣

28
00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:23.956
In the same year, we were ready.
同在这一年，我们也做好了准备

29
00:01:23.980 --> 00:01:27.076
The year we lost our inhibition and moved with courageous abandon
我们失去了家园，带着勇气的流放去前进

30
00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:29.596
was also the year we stared down barrels,
同时，我们对阻碍怒目而视

31
00:01:29.620 --> 00:01:31.956
sang of cranes in skies, ducked and parried,
歌颂高飞的鹤群回避并闪躲着

32
00:01:31.980 --> 00:01:34.436
caught gold in hijab, collected death threats,
火中取栗，视死如归

33
00:01:34.460 --> 00:01:35.796
knew ourselves as patriots,
我们知道自己是爱国者，

34
00:01:35.820 --> 00:01:39.036
said, "We're 35 now, time we settled down and found a running mate,"
说，“我们三十五岁了，是时候静下心来，寻找伴侣，”

35
00:01:39.060 --> 00:01:42.196
made road maps for infant joy, shamed nothing but fear,
追求天伦之乐，问心无愧但仍心有所惧

36
00:01:42.220 --> 00:01:44.476
called ourselves fat and meant, of course,
我们称自己身材肥硕，不过当然，是指

37
00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:45.716
impeccable.
完美无瑕

38
00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:47.676
This year, we were women,
这一年，我们是女人，

39
00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:49.476
not brides or trinkets,
而非新娘或是饰品，

40
00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:50.996
not an off-brand gender,
不是粗陋的性别，

41
00:01:51.020 --> 00:01:53.156
not a concession, but women.
不是一味让步，而是女人。

42
00:01:53.180 --> 00:01:54.476
Instruct your babies.
指引你的孩子。

43
00:01:54.500 --> 00:01:57.876
Remind them that the year has passed to be docile or small.
提醒他们，被驯化和轻视的年代已经过去。

44
00:01:57.900 --> 00:02:00.516
Some of us said for the first time that we were women,
有些人说，这是我们第一次身为女人

45
00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:02.916
