严肃对待这个团结的誓言。

46
00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:05.196
Some of us bore children and some of us did not,
我们中的一些人养育了儿女，一些没有，

47
00:02:05.220 --> 00:02:07.636
and none of us questioned whether that made us real
却无人问及这是否是让我们真实

48
00:02:07.660 --> 00:02:09.436
or appropriate or true.
亦或是得体，或者正确

49
00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:11.596
When she asks you of this year,
当她问及你这一年，

50
00:02:11.620 --> 00:02:14.525
your daughter, whether your offspring or heir to your triumph,
您的女儿，无论是您的子嗣或者接班人，

51
00:02:14.549 --> 00:02:17.556
from her comforted side of history teetering towards woman,
从她对女性历史理解的角度上，

52
00:02:17.580 --> 00:02:19.876
